FBIS4-16310 "drsov073_b_94018" FBIS-SOV-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Aeroflot Privatization Decision Signed Aeroflot Privatization Decision Signed LD1404183394 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 0025 GMT 14 Apr 94 LD1404183394 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] Vitaliy Yefimov, the Russian Federation's minister of trancport, has told RIA that the government of the Russian Federation has signed a decision on the flotation of the Aeroflot Russian International Airlines air company. He said that the decision was signed two days ago and noted that, under the document, each of Aeroflot's four subsidiary companies can now regard itself as independent. However, Vladimir Potapov, president of Aeroflot's international division, told RIA that he had not seen the document relating to the airline's flotation and, therefore, could not comment on it.
